        "$:/plugins/ihm/bible/readme": {
            "text": "!Quick start\nTo show a bible quote in block mode:\n``<<bqb Gen 1,1>>``\n\nDisplays as:\n<<bqb Gen 1,1>>\n\nFor inline bible quotes you can do something like this:\n\n``In the bible it says that God created the heavens and the earth, the latin says <<bqi Gen 1,1>>``\n\nIt display as:\n\nIn the bible it says that God created the heavens and the earth, the latin says <<bqi Gen 1,1>>.\n\n!More options\nYou can specify the translation to be used:\n``<<bqb Gen 1,1 NAB>>``\n\n<<bqb Gen 1,1 NAB>>\n\n!Configuration\n|!Tiddler |!Description |\n|$:/config/ihm/bible/defaultTranslation |The translation to be used if none is specified |\n|$:/config/ihm/bible/verseSeparator |The character to use to separate chapter from verse number |",
